      <p class="pf-sub">Fixed prices. System balanced on completion. Our own Gas Safe engineers. Wirral property knowledge. All CH postcodes covered.</p>
      <div class="pf-why-grid">
        <div class="pf-why-item"><h3>Fixed Price Before We Start</h3><p>Every other Wirral radiator company asks you to call for a quote. We publish our prices and they are fixed. The price we quote is the price on the invoice. No additions on the day, no surprises after the work is done.</p></div>
